{"tid":1486243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當一切平靜之後,政府會與市民展開真誠對話","createTime":"2019-08-18T21:49:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T22:25:57.000Z","uid":129989,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"968751719dd32880c1cb606391127cc2b5e5ab3b","tid":1486243,"uid":129989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T21:49:46.000Z","msg":"17 20 雙普選權利被受到港共 中共政府既剝削<br />\n憑乜野要香港人同佢傾 <br />\n我地既基本權利被剝削 我地仲可以同佢地溝通 妥協 <br />\n仲有得妥協咩 仲有退路可以退咩<div style=\"text-align: right;\">梁天椅</div><br />\n依家仲要我地先放低武器 先同我地傾??<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">傾你老母</span><br />\n要我地先認輸再比你施捨??<br />\n雖然佢都唔係第一次講 但係訓唔著今日睇返以前既片 有感而發<br />\n香港人 我地今次唔會再輸<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">希望大家仲記得梁天椅</span>"},{"pid":"c00d90e701d933d5e75d768c25020ef7987f1d96","tid":1486243,"uid":19055,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T21:52:08.000Z","msg":"係你教識我和平遊行係冇用<br />\n準備行動升級"},{"pid":"62e9c051d465ce6cefbbdc4d96b339b27bc6acfc","tid":1486243,"uid":129989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T21:52:23.000Z","msg":"希望大家可以叫醒埋身邊既港豬 香港人無得再退"},{"pid":"98a2fb6aea78a31ebafb440867b15c52385c0ed2","tid":1486243,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T21:53:28.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />借個位<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不要說「推」，試著說「８２３人鏈」<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2dzjyo4yc2sta.cloudfront.net/?url=images.pitchero.com/ui/2245472/image_5ae228ce3a90a.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;h=128&amp;t=square\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2dzjyo4yc2sta.cloudfront.net%2F%3Furl%3Dimages.pitchero.com%2Fui%2F2245472%2Fimage_5ae228ce3a90a.jpg%26w%3D128%26h%3D128%26t%3Dsquare&h=73f103df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n８